OL,3,CTasers to be trialled in prisons after
OL,4,Cbrother of arena bomber attacked guards
OL,6,FThe use of tasers in prisons will be
OL,7,Ftrialled after the brother of the
OL,8,FManchester Arena bomber attacked
OL,9,Fguards with hot oil and home-made
OL,10,Fweapons at HMP Frankland, the Justice
OL,11,FSecretary has said.
OL,13,FFour prison officers were injured at
OL,14,Fthe jail in Durham by Manchester bomb
OL,15,Fplotter Hashem Abedi, with three taken
OL,16,Fto hospital earlier this month.
