OL,3,CTasers to be trialled in prisons after
OL,4,Cbrother of arena bomber attacked guards
OL,6,FShabana Mahmood previously announced
OL,7,Fthe Prison Service will investigate
OL,8,Fwhether frontline staff should be
OL,9,Fgiven protective body armour and the
OL,10,FMinistry of Justice has pledged to
OL,11,Fcarry out a review following the
OL,12,Fincident.
OL,14,FIt comes after union bosses called for
OL,15,Fofficers to be given stab vests and
OL,16,Fprotective equipment, arguing the
OL,17,Fincident shows "how dangerous our job
OL,18,Fis".
