OL,3,CTasers to be trialled in prisons after
OL,4,Cbrother of arena bomber attacked guards
OL,6,FSpeaking in the Commons on Tuesday, Ms
OL,7,FMahmood said: "The House will be aware
OL,8,Fof the attack at HMP Frankland on the
OL,9,F12 of April.
OL,11,F"The bravery of the officers involved
OL,12,Fthat day undoubtedly saved lives, my
OL,13,Fthoughts are with them as they recover.
OL,15,F"I think also of the victims of the
OL,16,FManchester Arena bombing and their
OL,17,Ffamilies who are understandably
OL,18,Foutraged.
