OL,3,CTasers to be trialled in prisons after
OL,4,Cbrother of arena bomber attacked guards
OL,6,F"Since the attack, I have suspended
OL,7,Faccess to kitchens in separation
OL,8,Fcentres and in close supervision
OL,9,Fcentres.
OL,11,F"Alongside that, an independent review
OL,12,Fwill ascertain how this incident was
OL,13,Fable to happen, what more must be done
OL,14,Fto protect prison staff and, more
OL,15,Fwidely, how separation centres are run.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
