OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F396A1745420388
OL,3,CTasers to be trialled in prisons after
OL,4,Cbrother of arena bomber attacked guards
OL,6,F"The Prison Service will also conduct
OL,7,Fa snap review of the use of protective
OL,8,Fbodily armour. In addition, I can
OL,9,Ftoday announce that HMPPS (HM Prison
OL,10,Fand Probation Service) will trial the
OL,11,Fuse of tasers in our prisons.
OL,13,F"Wherever we can strengthen our
OL,14,Fdefences, to better protect our staff
OL,15,Fand the public, we will do so."
